-- Merkel Says German Agreement on Greek Financial Rescue May Take a Few Days
-- John Fraher
-- 2010-04-26T13:21:43Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-04-26/merkel-says-german-agreement-on-greek-financial-rescue-may-take-a-few-days.html

          
          
             German Chancellor Angela Merkel
said Greece needs to show its budget is on a “sustainable”
path and a full German agreement to a bailout may take “a few
days.” She made the remarks in a statement in Berlin.  
